snippet.textDisplay: I want to start with, I absolutely adore you and respect your knowledge of makeup. I’m a 22 year old single mom of two, currently in school, and really just struggling to make ends meat. I literally own one thing of mascara, a set of false lashes, one lipstick, and (my prized makeup possession) one of your highlighters gifted to me by my sister. I know you’ve made videos about it before, but I was wondering if I could get a list of your most approved/cheapest makeup necessities. I struggle with my self image/worth and when I actually get to borrow someone’s makeup to do a full face it really helps. Thank you for all you do for your fans and I am so proud of all you have accomplished. Also, thank you to you and Nate for letting us into your lives and entertaining us all as you two do. 💋
